	<div class = "bpa-feature-content page-common-padding clearfix">
		<div class = "f-medium bpa-feature feature-header bold padding0 col-md-4">Features of Building Plan Approval System</div>
	
		<div class = "f-regular bpa-card-cont col-md-4">
			<div class = "bpa-feature-card card">
				<div class = "card-body">
					<div class = "feature-icon-cont">
						<div class = "feature-icon-background center-align-flex">
							<img class="feature-icon" src = "/egi/resources/guide/assets/ICONS/BPA_1.png"/>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class = "feature-heading">End to End Process Digitisation</div>
					<div class = "feature-description">
						Scrutiny reports are produced in the matter of minutes with automatic rule mapping. The development regulation process is also automated saving paperwork and time of stakeholders.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class = "f-regular bpa-card-cont col-md-4">
			<div class = "bpa-feature-card card">
				<div class = "card-body">
					<div class = "feature-icon-cont">
						<div class = "feature-icon-background center-align-flex">
							<img class="feature-icon" src="/egi/resources/guide/assets/ICONS/BPA_2.png" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class = "feature-heading">Single window for multiple services</div>
					<div class = "feature-description">
						Stakeholders like ULB officials, architects, town planners, engineers and citizens are connected on a single platform to coordinate various services. Stakeholders are updated in real time of the application progress thus achieving transparency.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class = "f-regular padding0 col-md-4">
			<div class = "bpa-feature-card card">
				<div class = "card-body">
					<div class = "feature-icon-cont">
					 	<div class = "feature-icon-background center-align-flex">
					 		<img class="feature-icon" src="/egi/resources/guide/assets/ICONS/BPA_3.png" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class = "feature-heading">Open source smart platform</div>
					<div class = "feature-description">
						It is a state-of-the-art, ERP-based platform created for urban governance, built on advanced open source technologies ensuring flexibility, interoperability and faster implementation.

					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class = "f-regular bpa-card-cont col-md-4">
			<div class = "bpa-feature-card card">
